        <item>
            <title>v1.1.3</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2026 09:44:51 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>3</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.2</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <link>https://github.com/arcanii/SQLTerminal/releases/tag/v1.1.3</link>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>SQLTerminal 1.1.3</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Responsive UI</b> — queries run off the main thread, so a slow or network query no longer freezes the app; cancel a running query with <b>⌘.</b></li>
                    <li><b>PostgreSQL SSL/TLS</b> (Off / Prefer / Require) with a status-bar lock when the connection is encrypted, plus a click-through connection-details popover.</li>
                    <li><b>Schema sidebar</b> — browse tables and columns; click a table to insert a <code>SELECT</code>.</li>
                    <li><b>Run selection</b>, or the statement under the cursor, with <b>⌘↩</b>.</li>
                    <li><b>Safety</b> — read-only mode, and confirmation before <code>DROP</code> / <code>TRUNCATE</code> / <code>WHERE</code>-less <code>DELETE</code>/<code>UPDATE</code>.</li>
                    <li><b>Transactions</b> — Begin / Commit / Rollback from the toolbar.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
