        <item>
            <title>v0.1.2</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.1.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>26.2</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <link>https://github.com/arcanii/SQLTerminal/releases/tag/v0.1.2</link>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>SQLTerminal 0.1.2</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Automatic updates via Sparkle, with a <b>Check for Updates…</b> menu item.</li>
                    <li>PostgreSQL: connection errors now show the server's real reason (and suggest the <code>pg_hba.conf</code> line for "no entry" rejections); the connection sheet shows every field at once and remembers your engine; <code>.use</code>/<code>.connect</code> switch databases with clear "no access" messages.</li>
                    <li>Selectable text in the output pane.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
